body.source:
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CHTR.DA_CITY_TO_COUNTY
/* Generated on 20-JAN-15 03.39.45.504496000 PM -06:00 */
AS

PROCEDURE add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,city_id IN NUMBER
,county_id IN NUMBER
,primary_rollup_ind IN VARCHAR2
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_city_to_county.add, parms=' || city_id || '|' || county_id || '|' || primary_rollup_ind || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_city_to_county a
(
a.city_id
,a.county_id
,a.primary_rollup_ind
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
add.city_id
,add.county_id
,add.primary_rollup_ind
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
);
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_city_to_county.add');

END add;

PROCEDURE del (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,city_id IN NUMBER
,county_id IN NUMBER
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_city_to_county.del, parms=' || city_id || '|' || county_id || '|' || audit_user || '|');
UPDATE chtr.t_city_to_county a
SET a.record_stat = 'D'
,a.modified_dttm = SYSTIMESTAMP
,a.modified_by = del.audit_user
WHERE a.city_id = del.city_id
AND a.county_id = del.county_id
;
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_city_to_county.del');

END del;

END da_city_to_county;
